《'''HOME'''》是[[韓國|韓國]]男歌手[[Roy_Kim|Roy Kim]]第2張正規韓語專輯，於2014年10月8日由[[CJ_E&M|CJ E&M]]發行，主打歌曲為專輯同名歌曲《Home》<ref name="Release"/>。

==背景==
2014年2月，當Roy Kim尚在[[喬治城大學|喬治城大學]]就讀時，[[CJ_E&M|CJ E&M]]宣布已與Roy Kim續約，並準備在秋天發行新專輯<ref>{{cite web| title=Roy Kim to Return with a New Album in Autumn| url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/59369/roykim-to-make-fall-comeback| publisher=CJ E&M enewsWorld| accessdate=2014-09-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017172907/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/59369/roykim-to-make-fall-comeback| archive-date=2014-10-17| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。同年6月，他在向歌迷親筆書寫的信件中表示他正努力製作新專輯：「I'm preparing my second album so please just wait a little more!」<ref>{{cite web| title=Roy Kim Expresses His Desire to Return to Stage in Handwritten Letter to Fans| url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/68361/roykim-writes-a-letter-to-fans| publisher=CJ E&M enewsWorld| accessdate=2014-09-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017172903/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/68361/roykim-writes-a-letter-to-fans| archive-date=2014-10-17| dead-url=yes}}，語句為英語翻譯</ref>9月時，官方公佈專輯正式定名為《HOME》，並確定10月發行<ref>{{cite web| title=Roy Kim to Make Comeback with Second Album in October| url=http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/76384/roykim-to-return-this-fall| publisher=CJ E&M enewsWorld| accessdate=2014-09-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925042241/http://mwave.interest.me/enewsworld/en/article/76384/roykim-to-return-this-fall| archive-date=2014-09-25| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

《HOME》邀請了眾多音樂人參與，包括埃里克·達爾肯（Eric Darken）、丹·李約瑟（Dan Needham）、{{link-en|白心樂隊|White Heart|加里·倫恩}}（Gary Lunn）、馬克·烏塞利（Mark Uselli）和[[鄭晟河|鄭晟河]]等。<ref>{{cite web|title=Roy Kim to Release 2nd Album ‘Home’ in October|url=http://www.mnetamerica.com/news/article/76984/roykim-confirms-album-release-date|publisher=Mnet America|accessdate=2014-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006101045/http://www.mnetamerica.com/news/article/76984/roykim-confirms-album-release-date|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=Roy Kim shares a handwritten album tracklist for his upcoming album 'Home'| url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2014/09/roy-kim-shares-a-handwritten-album-tracklist-for-his-upcoming-album-home| publisher=[[Allkpop|Allkpop]]| accessdate=2014-10-02| archive-date=2014-09-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140930203653/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2014/09/roy-kim-shares-a-handwritten-album-tracklist-for-his-upcoming-album-home| dead-url=no}}</ref>

==發行==
2014年9月21日，Roy Kim在其官方[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道上載了前一張專輯《{{link-en|Love Love Love (Roy Kim專輯)|Love Love Love (Roy Kim album)|Love Love Love}}》中的《12 o'clock》之原音樂版本，說明「二輯即將來臨。下個滿月」（2nd album coming real soon. Next full moon），並通知歌迷專輯即將發行<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LMFvg8rVByw| title=12 o'clock - Roy Kim 로이킴 열두시| format=YouTube| author=Roy Kim| date=2014-09-21| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2017-07-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703171453/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LMFvg8rVByw| dead-url=no}}</ref>，而專輯宣傳照連同發行日期（10月8日）同時在9月29日披露<ref>{{cite web|title=Roy Kim Reveals Teaser Photo and Release Date for His Second Album, “Home”|url=http://www.soompi.com/2014/09/28/roy-kim-reveals-teaser-photo-and-release-date-for-his-second-album-home/|publisher=Soompi|accessdate=2014-09-29|archive-date=2014-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141002012559/http://www.soompi.com/2014/09/28/roy-kim-reveals-teaser-photo-and-release-date-for-his-second-album-home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，Roy Kim在他的個人[[Instagram|Instagram]]中張貼了一張手寫曲目名單<ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴, 자필 트랙리스트 깜짝 공개 '손글씨에서조차 느껴지는 가을 내음'| url=http://enews24.interest.me/news/article.asp?nsID=514011| publisher=eNews World| accessdate=2014-09-29| archive-date=2014-10-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006072642/http://enews24.interest.me/news/article.asp?nsID=514011| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=roykimmusic on Instagram| url=http://instagram.com/p/tjFK3iTe0v| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2014-10-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020073852/http://instagram.com/p/tjFK3iTe0v| dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在10月2日發放了主打曲《Home》音樂錄影帶的宣傳片<ref>{{cite web| title=Roy Kim hints at a dramatic story line to come with MV teaser for 'Home'| url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2014/10/roy-kim-hints-at-a-dramatic-story-line-to-come-with-mv-teaser-for-home| publisher=Allkpop| accessdate=2014-10-02| archive-date=2014-10-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004093408/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2014/10/roy-kim-hints-at-a-dramatic-story-line-to-come-with-mv-teaser-for-home| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n4yIL8AY2LM| title=로이킴 (Roy Kim) - HOME (Teaser)| format=YouTube| author=CJENMMUSIC Official| date=2014-10-01| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2014-10-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141002112827/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n4yIL8AY2LM&gl=US&hl=en| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

專輯發行之前，《即使沒有永遠》（{{lang-ko|영원한 건 없지만}}）的歌詞影片在CJ E&M官方YouTube頻道公開<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JRS28BaQjs| title=로이킴 (Roy Kim) - 영원한 건 없지만 (Nothing Lasts Forever) MV| format=YouTube| author=CJENMMUSIC Official| date=2014-10-07| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2014-10-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021023701/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JRS28BaQjs&list=PLwBXPtjuNGOAKRxr5MEaWEJleBlUK41LT| dead-url=no}}</ref>，這影片由[[天文攝影|天文攝影]]家[[權五哲|權五哲]]（{{lang-ko|권오철}}）運用[[縮時攝影|縮時攝影]]拍攝了[[極光|極光]]的片段，並在10月3日到10月7日在[[世宗文化會館|世宗文化會館]]免費播放<ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴과 천체사진가의 만남…'영원한건 없지만' 이색 선공개| url=http://www.mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=201410031137341117&ext=na| publisher=mydaily| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2014-10-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028190144/http://www.mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=201410031137341117&ext=na| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴, ‘영원한 건 없지만’ MV 전시회서 선공개| url=http://news.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=20141003000118&md=20141006003811_BK| publisher=[[The_Korean_Herald|Herald Economy Korea]]| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2016-03-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230208/http://news.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=20141003000118&md=20141006003811_BK| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

整張專輯在[[韩国标准时|韓國時間]]10月8日午夜12時數碼發行，同時主打歌的《Home》音樂錄影帶也公開<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=czdxV99r89Y| title=로이킴 (Roy Kim) - Home MV| format=YouTube| author=CJENMMUSIC Official| date=2014-10-08| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2014-10-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021023706/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=czdxV99r89Y&list=PLwBXPtjuNGOAKRxr5MEaWEJleBlUK41LT| dead-url=no}}</ref>。發行不久，《Home》登上了各大韓國實時音樂流行榜的首位，包括[[MelOn|MelOn]]、Mnet、Naver Music、Olleh Music及Monkey3等<ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴, 신곡 '홈'으로 차트 접수…김동률과 어깨 나란히| url=http://news.tf.co.kr/read/entertain/1427346.htm| publisher=The Fact| accessdate=2014-10-07| archive-date=2014-10-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012183528/http://news.tf.co.kr/read/entertain/1427346.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月14日，官方在YouTube頻道特別發布了《秋天》（{{lang-ko|가을에}}）的{{link-en|一鏡到尾|One shot (music video)|一鏡到尾音樂錄影帶}}<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p72drSSffXg| title=로이킴 - 가을에 (When Autumn Comes) MV| format=YouTube| author=CJENMMUSIC Official| date=2014-10-14| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2014-10-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014150242/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p72drSSffXg&gl=US&hl=en| dead-url=no}}</ref>，由拍攝《Home》音樂錄影帶的導演[[宋元永|宋元永]]（{{lang-ko|송원영}}）操刀製作<ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴 '가을에' 뮤비 공개, 슬로우 원테이크 기법 활용 '독특'| url=http://news1.kr/articles/?1903532| publisher=News1 Korea| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2014-10-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020024707/http://news1.kr/articles/?1903532| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==宣傳==
Roy Kim在專輯發行以後立即不同音樂節目中為歌曲宣傳，回歸舞台在《[[M!_Countdown|M! Countdown]]》舉行<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8t566o2vj4| title=Mnet [M COUNTDOWN] Ep.397 : 로이킴(Roy Kim) - HOME @MCOUNTDOWN_141009| format=YouTube| author=Mnet| date=2014-10-10| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2016-03-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309210333/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8t566o2vj4| dead-url=no}}</ref>，隨後在《{{link-en|Wave K|Wave K}}》<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5E1K-m9Fj4| title=Simply K-Pop EP 132 -Roy Kim - Home 로이 킴 - Home| format=YouTube| author=ARIRANG KPOP| date=2014-10-10| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2016-03-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309093911/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5E1K-m9Fj4| dead-url=no}}</ref> 、《[[KBS音乐银行|KBS音乐银行]]》<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8dd1RsmqlqY| title=[HIT] 뮤직뱅크-로이 킴(Roy Kim) - Home.20141010| format=YouTube| author=KBSKpop| date=2014-10-11| accessdate=2014-10-16| archive-date=2016-03-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309065851/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8dd1RsmqlqY| dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[Show_Champion|Show Champion]]》也進行了演出。

同時，專輯同名演唱會《2014 ROYKIM LIVE TOUR HOME》於10月25日在[[奧林匹克公園_(首爾)|首爾奧林匹克公園]]奧林匹克館舉行，其後也會在11月前於[[大邱廣域市|大邱]]、[[大田广域市|大田]]、[[釜山廣域市|釜山]]與[[昌原市|昌原]]舉行宣傳專輯的演唱會。<ref>{{ko icon}} {{cite web| title=로이킴, 2014 라이브 투어 'HOME' 포스터 공개| url=http://www.asiatoday.co.kr/view.php?key=20140925000853224| publisher=Asia Today| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2014-10-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020021357/http://www.asiatoday.co.kr/view.php?key=20140925000853224| dead-url=no}}</ref>

